Introduction

My Darling (Korean: 마이달링) was a South Korean girl group under NES Entertainment. Originally as four, they debuted on April 26, 2018 with their first single "Dramatic". They presumably disbanded in later 2020 as their SNS accounts have been inactive since October 2020.
